[normal]orthamptonshire County Council ha
[normal]s 
[normal]introduced 
[normal]a 
[normal]Revolving
[normal] 
[normal]I
[normal]nfrast
[normal]ructure 
[normal]F
[normal]und
[normal] based on the following general principles: 
[normal]This approach has allowed a £100m programme of projects to commence as a result of up
[normal]front funding in the order of only £10m. 
